<body lang=EN-ID style='tab-interval:36.0pt;word-wrap:break-word'>

<div class=WordSection1>

<div style='margin-bottom:37.5pt'>

<h1 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:windowtext'>DOKUMEN DESAIN
&amp; IMPLEMENTASI<o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<h2 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:windowtext'>TUGAS BESAR
PRAKTIKUM RPL 2<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h2 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:windowtext'>Richard Firmansyah
(714240047)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h2 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:windowtext'>Zidan Haira
Ramadhan (714240047)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:center'><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<h3 align=center style='text-align:center'><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Kelompok 3: API Gateway / Integrator<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

</div>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>1. Deskripsi Singkat Sistem<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>API Gateway bertindak sebagai
pintu masuk utama (Single Entry Point) untuk seluruh ekosistem UMKM (7
Aplikasi). Gateway ini menggunakan bahasa pemrograman Golang dengan framework
Gin dan database PostgreSQL. Seluruh komunikasi antar-aplikasi wajib melalui
gateway ini untuk memastikan keamanan, pencatatan transaksi, dan penerapan
aturan bisnis (seperti pemotongan fee).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>2. Peran &amp; Tanggung Jawab (Fungsi Utama)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Sesuai dengan spesifikasi
tugas besar, API Gateway kami memiliki peran berikut:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>API
     Routing:</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Meneruskan (proxy) <i>request</i>
     dari user atau service lain ke aplikasi tujuan (SmartBank, Marketplace,
     POS, LogistiKita, SupplierHub, UMKM Insight).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Validasi
     Keamanan:</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Mengecek validitas Token JWT
     pada setiap <i>request</i> yang masuk sebelum diteruskan ke service
     tujuan.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Pencatatan
     (Logging):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Mencatat seluruh aktivitas <i>request</i>
     dan <i>response</i> secara <i>asynchronous</i> ke dalam database
     PostgreSQL.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Manajemen
     Biaya (Gateway Fee):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Memotong saldo sebesar <b>0.5%</b>
     dari setiap transaksi antar-aplikasi yang melalui gateway.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Rate
     Limiting:</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Mengatur batas akses dengan
     memberlakukan jeda waktu (<i>cooldown</i>) 10-30 detik antar transaksi dan
     batas maksimal 10 transaksi per hari untuk setiap <i>user</i>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Service
     Registry &amp; Health Check:</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Mencatat aplikasi mana saja
     yang aktif dan memantau status kesehatannya (hidup/mati).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>3. Arsitektur Sistem &amp; Alur Komunikasi<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p><b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Pola Komunikasi (Hub and
Spoke):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><br>
Semua aplikasi tidak diperbolehkan berkomunikasi langsung satu sama lain (P2P),
melainkan harus melalui API Gateway.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p><b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Alur Request:</span></b><span
style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>User /
     Service A mengirim request ke </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>http://[IP-Gateway]:8080/api/[Service-Tujuan]/[Endpoint]</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gateway
     memvalidasi Token JWT.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gateway
     mengecek Rate Limit (Cooldown &amp; Max Limit).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gateway
     mencatat Log Request.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Jika
     valid, Gateway meneruskan request ke aplikasi tujuan.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gateway
     menghitung dan mencatat Fee 0.5% (jika request merupakan transaksi
     keuangan).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Gateway
     mengembalikan response ke User / Service A.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>4. Struktur Database (PostgreSQL)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Gateway mengelola 4 tabel
utama secara mandiri (terpisah dari aplikasi lain):<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>request_logs</span></code><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Menyimpan history lalu lintas API (Request ID, target, IP, status, waktu
     respons).<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>gateway_fee_transactions</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Mencatat nominal transaksi asli, potongan fee 0.5%, status transaksi, dan
     service asal-tujuan.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>service_registries</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Menyimpan URL dan status aplikasi dalam ekosistem.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>rate_limit_records</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>:
     Mencatat riwayat transaksi harian <i>user</i> untuk penerapan <i>cooldown</i>
     dan limitasi.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>5. Daftar API Endpoint Gateway<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<table class=MsoNormalTable border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"
 style='width:100.0%;border-collapse:collapse;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184'>
 <tr style='mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes'>
  <td style='border:solid black 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .75pt;
  background:#D9E1F2;padding:6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:
  15.0pt;margin-left:0cm'><b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext'>Kategori</span></b><b><span
  style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:
  solid black .75pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .75pt;background:#D9E1F2;
  padding:6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:
  15.0pt;margin-left:0cm'><b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext'>Method</span></b><b><span
  style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:
  solid black .75pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .75pt;background:#D9E1F2;
  padding:6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:
  15.0pt;margin-left:0cm'><b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
  mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext'>Endpoint</span></b><b><span
  style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
  </td>
  <td style='border:solid black 1.0pt;border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:
  solid black .75pt;mso-border-alt:solid black .75pt;background:#D9E1F2;
  padding:6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:
