<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>6. Contoh URL Proxy (Routing)<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>Untuk mengakses service lain
melalui Gateway, struktur URL-nya adalah </span><code><span style='font-size:
10.0pt'>/api/[nama-service]/[path]</span></code><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif'>:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

