<h2><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";
color:windowtext'>7. Pemenuhan Aturan Spreadsheet<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Aturan #5
     (Single Entry Point):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Terpenuhi dengan adanya
     endpoint proxy.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Aturan #6
     (JWT &amp; Logging):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Terpenuhi dengan </span><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>JWTAuthMiddleware</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     dan </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>LoggingMiddleware</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Aturan #10
     (Gateway Fee 0.5%):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Terpenuhi pada logic </span><code><span
     style='font-size:10.0pt'>FeeService</span></code><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> dan
     tersimpan di database.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Aturan #15
     &amp; #16 (Cooldown &amp; Max Tx):</span></b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Terpenuhi
     melalui </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>RateLimitMiddleware</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
     yang divalidasi per <i>user</i>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><b><span style='font-family:
     "Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Aturan #25
     (Database Sendiri):</span></b><span style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;
     mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> Terpenuhi menggunakan skema
     PostgreSQL </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>api_gateway</span></code><span
     style='font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

